posts.post_title: WTB/WTTF - SF Hess N333 Newsboys League
posts.post_content:
Looking for N333 SF Hess Newsboys League cards from all teams:

Albany Daily Press & Knickerbocker (Albany, NY)
Boston Globe (Boston, MA)
Cleveland Plain Dealer (Cleveland, OH)
Detroit Journal (Detroit, MI)
NY World (New York City, NY)
Philadelphia Call  /  The Call (Philadelphia, PA)
Rochester Post-Express (Rochester, NY)
Syracuse Herald (Syracuse, NY)

Bold Text matches team name as it appears on card, Philadelphia cards are anonymous with no nameplates.

Generous cash and/or trade material available.

[url]detroitwolverines@gmail.com[/url]

I've been able to pick up several Newsboys since last post, paying and trading with strong offers.

Would enjoy understanding what may be out there regardless of whether it is held tight or available for sale/trade.  Show me the N333s :)

Bump into 2016 . . .

Still need a couple team examples (Albany & NY City) and interested in all Detroit cards.

Looking for example cards from Albany & New York; looking for all the Detroits . . .  any idea where these examples reside (from old auctions) ??
